00:13:23.480 --> 00:13:24.200
Eles.

00:13:24.800 --> 00:13:26.680
Levem Jiang Lin e o Diretor Xia para o exterior.

00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:28.280
Entregue-os à polícia.

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:30.280
Não toque no meu marido!

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:30.840
Pare com isso!

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:32.060
Solte-me!

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:32.920
Jian Lin!

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:33.360
Siyue.

00:13:33.360 --> 00:13:33.760
Jian Lin!

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:34.320
Siyue!

00:13:34.320 --> 00:13:35.040
Jian Lin!

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:35.840
Mãe!

00:13:35.840 --> 00:13:36.840
Senhora Ye, deixe-me explicar! A Sra. Ye!

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:37.520
Jian Lin!

